{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-working-with-text/working-with-text-lesson-d","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"top-working-with-text","challengeType":15,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Funkcija <code>em</code> čini tekst kursivnim (italic). Takođe dodaje semantički naglasak tekstu, što može uticati na stvari kao što su čitači ekrana. Da biste definisali naglašenu funkciju, obavijte sadržaj teksta unutar oznake <code>&#x3C;em></code>.</p>\n<p>Da biste koristili samo <code>em</code>:</p>\n<iframe allowfullscreen=\"true\" allowpaymentrequest=\"true\" allowtransparency=\"true\" class=\"cp_embed_iframe \" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"300\" width=\"100%\" name=\"cp_embed_6\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://codepen.io/TheOdinProjectExamples/embed/wvewqpp?height=300&amp;theme-id=dark&amp;default-tab=html%2Cresult&amp;slug-hash=wvewqpp&amp;user=TheOdinProjectExamples&amp;name=cp_embed_6\" style=\"width: 100%; overflow:hidden; display:block;\" title=\"CodePen Embed\" loading=\"lazy\" id=\"cp_embed_wvewqpp\"></iframe>\n<p>Zdravo, kao element od <code>strong</code>, videćete da koristite više funkciju od <code>em</code> uz druge tekstualne elemente:</p>\n<iframe allowfullscreen=\"true\" allowpaymentrequest=\"true\" allowtransparency=\"true\" class=\"cp_embed_iframe \" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"300\" width=\"100%\" name=\"cp_embed_7\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://codepen.io/TheOdinProjectExamples/embed/VwWZzyj?height=300&amp;theme-id=dark&amp;default-tab=html%2Cresult&amp;slug-hash=VwWZzyj&amp;user=TheOdinProjectExamples&amp;name=cp_embed_7\" style=\"width: 100%; overflow:hidden; display:block;\" title=\"CodePen Embed\" loading=\"lazy\" id=\"cp_embed_VwWZzyj\"></iframe>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Odin","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-working-with-text/working-with-text-lesson-d"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Koju funkciju treba da koristite da učinite tekst kursivnim (italic) radi naglašavanja?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><code>&#x3C;strong>This is an italic message&#x3C;/strong></code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>&#x3C;em>This is an italic message&#x3C;/em></code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>&#x3C;italic>This is an italic message&#x3C;/italic></code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null}],"solution":2}],"scene":null,"superBlock":"the-odin-project","tests":[],"title":"Rad sa tekstom za obuku D","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/the-odin-project/#top-working-with-text","dashedName":"working-with-text-lesson-d","certification":"the-odin-project","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"the-odin-project","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"top-working-with-text","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-working-with-text/working-with-text-lesson-e","prevChallengePath":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-working-with-text/working-with-text-lesson-c","id":"637f4e6e72c65bc8e73dfe2a","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":15,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-working-with-text/working-with-text-lesson-d"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}